  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria: All injured patients &gt; 15 years old who are brought or present to the
        The Alfred Trauma Centre during the study period.

        Exclusion Criteria: Stable Trauma patients (ie Pulse rate &lt;100/minute, MAP &gt;70mmHg, Hb &gt;70,
        temperature &gt;35 and &lt;37.5, Spo2 &gt;92%, GCS &gt;13) undergoing secondary transfer from another
        hospital, where trauma occurred &gt;6hrs prior to arrival.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
